<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/main.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <title>Home page</title>
</head>
<style>   

    #survey {
        font-weight: 100;
    }

    img {
        border-radius: 30px; 
        max-height: 300px;
        object-fit: cover;    
    }

    .col {
        padding-right: 4%;
        padding-left: 4%;
    }

    #module, #disclaimers {
        padding: 5%;
    }    

    /* input */
    input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 20px; /* Fully rounded border */
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Box shadow */
            margin: 15px 0px;
        }

    input[type="radio"] {
            width: 20px; /* Set the width of the radio button */
            height: 20px; /* Set the height of the radio button */
            border: 2px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 50%; /* Make the border fully rounded to create a circular shape */
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Box shadow */
            margin: 15px 5px;            
        }   

    .radioOptions {
        display: flex;
        margin-top: 1%;
        margin-bottom: 1%;
    }

    .radioLabel {        
        flex-basis: 15%;
        display: flex;                
    }

    .proceed-button {
        text-align: center;
        align-self: center;
        margin-top: 3%;        
    }

</style>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <header class="z-10">
        <%- include ('../partials/nav.ejs') %>
    </header>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="padded">
        <!-- Module -->
        <div id="module" class="card">  
            <!-- Row -->
            <div class="double-col">
                <!-- Image -->
                <div class="col w-2/5 imgDiv">
                    <img src="/images/<%= module %>.jpg" alt="Image sample" class="">
                </div>
                <!-- Heading + desc -->
                <div class="col w-3/5">
                    <h1 class=""><%=module.split('_').map(word => word.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + word.slice(1)).join(' ') %></h1>
                    <h2 id="survey" class="blue-text">Diagnostic Tool</h2>
                    <p class="mt-5"><%= desc %></p>            
                    <!-- Start quiz button -->
                    <a href="#disclaimers" class="blue-button w-1/3 mt-10">Start the quiz</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>      
        <!-- Disclaimers  -->
        <div id="disclaimers" class="">
            <h2 id="survey" class="blue-text mb-4">Disclaimers</h2>
            <p>The Circular Economy Measurement, Assessment, and Pathways (CE-MAP) diagnostic tool you are about to use results from government-funded research conducted by the Centre for Urban Transitions, Swinburne University of Technology. By proceeding with this assessment, you acknowledge and agree to the following terms:</p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>Data Usage: </strong>The Circular Economy Measurement, Assessment, and Pathways (CE-MAP) diagnostic tool you are about to use results from government-funded research conducted by the Centre for Urban Transitions, Swinburne University of Technology. By proceeding with this assessment, you acknowledge and agree to the following terms:</p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>Research Purposes: </strong>Your responses will contribute to ongoing research efforts to understand and advance the adoption of circular economy practices in various industries and sectors.</p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>Confidentiality: </strong>Your responses will remain confidential; no personally identifiable information will be shared or published. Your privacy is of utmost importance to us.</p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>Government Funding: </strong>The development of the CE-MAP diagnostic tool has been made possible through funding by the Victorian Government under the Victorian Circular Activator (VCA), and its purpose is to support sustainability and circular economy initiatives.</p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>Voluntary Participation: </strong>Participation in this assessment is entirely voluntary, and you can discontinue at any time. Your decision to participate or not will not affect your access to other services or resources.</p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>Results and Recommendations: </strong>The results and recommendations provided by the CE-MAP diagnostic tool are for informational and self-assessment purposes only. They are not binding, and you should consult with relevant experts and professionals before making any significant business decisions.</p>
            <br>
            <p>By clicking the <strong>"Begin Assessment"</strong> button or proceeding with the assessment, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this disclaimer and consent to using your data as described above.</p>
            <!-- Begin button -->
         
            <div class="proceed-button">
                <a href="#userForm"><button type="submit" class="blue-button w-1/5">Begin Assessment</button></a>         
            </div>
        </div>    

        
        <!-- Form -->
        <div id="userForm" class="form-container">
            <form action="/quiz/<%= module %>/start/" method="post">
    
                <label for="first_name">First Name:</label>
                <div class="name-input flex">
                    <input type="text" id="first_name" name="first_name" placeholder="First Name">
                    <input type="text" id="last_name" name="last_name" placeholder="Last Name">
                </div>
                
                <label for="org_name">Organisation Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="org_name" name="org_name" placeholder="Organisation Name">

                <label for="industry">Industry:</label>
                <input type="text" id="industry" name="industry" placeholder="Industry/sector">

                <label for="job_title">Job Title:</label>
                <input type="text" id="job_title" name="job_title" placeholder="Job Title/ Role">            
    
                <label for="email">Email Address:</label>
                <input type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address">

                <label for="years_of_experience">Years of Experience:</label>
                <input type="text" id="years_of_experience" name="years_of_experience" placeholder="Years of Experience">
    
                <label for="goal">Primary goal: (select one)</label>
                <div id="goal" class="radioOptions">
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="goal" value="Improve Sustainability">
                        <p>Improve Sustainability</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="goal" value="Enhance Profitability">
                        <p>Enhance Profitability</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">                    
                        <input type="radio" name="goal" value="Meet Regulatory Requirements">
                        <p>Meet Regulatory Requirements</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="goal" value="Enhance Brand Reputation">
                        <p>Enhance Brand Reputation</p>
                    </label>                                  
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="goal" value="Explore New Business Opportunities">
                        <p>Explore New Business Opportunities</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">                
                        <input type="radio" name="goal" value="Others">
                        <p>Others</p>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <label for="reason_of_use">What prompted you to use the CE-MAP diagnostic tool? (select one)</label>
                <div id="reason_of_use" class="radioOptions">
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="reason_of_use" value="Curiosity about Circular Economy">
                        <p>Curiosity about Circular Economy</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="reason_of_use" value="Seeking Sustainable Practices">
                        <p>Seeking Sustainable Practices</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">                    
                        <input type="radio" name="reason_of_use" value="Business Expansion">
                        <p>Business Expansion</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="reason_of_use" value="Regulatory Compliance">
                        <p>Regulatory Compliance</p>
                    </label>                                  
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="reason_of_use" value="Academic/Research Interest">
                        <p>Academic/Research Interest</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">                
                        <input type="radio" name="reason_of_use" value="Others">
                        <p>Others</p>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <label for="hear_about_us">How did you hear about the CE-MAP tool? (select one)</label>
                <div id="hear_about_us" class="radioOptions">
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="hear_about_us" value="Online Search">
                        <p>Online Search</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="hear_about_us" value="Referral from a Colleague">
                        <p>Referral from a Colleague </p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">                    
                        <input type="radio" name="hear_about_us" value="Social Media">
                        <p>Social Media</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="hear_about_us" value="Academic Institution">
                        <p>Academic Institution</p>
                    </label>                                  
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="hear_about_us" value="Government Initiative">
                        <p>Government Initiative</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">                
                        <input type="radio" name="hear_about_us" value="Others">
                        <p>Others</p>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <label for="enganged_in_ce">How did you hear about the CE-MAP tool? (select one)</label>
                <div id="enganged_in_ce" class="radioOptions">
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="enganged_in_ce" value="Yes">
                        <p>Yes</p>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radioLabel">
                        <input type="radio" name="enganged_in_ce" value="No">
                        <p>No </p>
                    </label>            
                </div>

                <label for="comments">Additional comments:</label>
                <input type="text" id="comments" name="comments" placeholder="Type your comments here">
    
                <!-- Next button -->
                <div class="proceed-button">
                    <button type="submit" class="blue-button w-1/5">Next</button>              
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>


    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="body">


        
    </div>

    
</body>
</html>

